/exec-plans/active/004-endpoint-console-schema-preview-ui.md:46:- Endpoint detail/editor pages can show generated MCP inputSchema preview.\ndocs/QUALITY_SCORE.md:27:| Runtime proof | Strong | db:prepare, start:smoke, start:logged |\ndocs/exec-plans/active/022-malformed-response-console-audit.md:48:- Endpoint console shows raw response evidence, elapsed time, matched case, and principal for malformed/failure cases.\ndocs/design-docs/core-beliefs.md:5:3. Endpoint permissions must be visible in OAuth consent and mechanically enforced in runtime calls.\ndocs/exec-plans/active/011-rest-tools-list-runtime.md:48:- Endpoint console can display REST list examples if useful without call execution.\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:9:- Preparation command: `npm run db:prepare`.\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:11:- Persistence source of truth: SQLite. `data/bootstrap-state.json` is no longer used by `db:prepare`.\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:13:## Endpoint\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:25:| `deleteCode` | `String?` | Endpoint delete-code storage for later protected delete flows. |\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:35:## EndpointParam\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:42:| `endpointId` | `String` | Required relation to `Endpoint`, cascades on endpoint delete. |\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:66:| `endpointId` | `String` | Required relation to `Endpoint`, cascades on endpoint delete. |\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:89:`npm run db:prepare` upserts one protected enabled endpoint:\ndocs/generated/db-schema.md:91:- Endpoint ID: `endpoint_default_echo`\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
